mages have one of the worst aggros imo...if i want to get summoned, i can make it happen in under 1 minute of a raid.... i dont have the lightning reflexes aa yet, so yea, i take a lot of damage....
<br />

<br />
but my advice to any magican out there... get HP gear... i have 5203 hp raid buffed, which isnt much compared to many of the top mages out there, but in a bot group, 5200hp is sometimes compairable to some of the monks / rogues / rangers you get in your groups.....i was in povalor one day, and the pally tanking for my group was having a hard time dealing with mobs unslowed, and i asked him how many hp he had (he had cleric buffs) and he was only at 5400....  <img src="images/smiles/icon_eek.gif" alt="Shocked" border="0" /> heh i almost wanted to tank for my group, if my ac was better rofl
<br />

