get lightning reflexes 5..but first get natural durabilty 3....it helps.... and also, casting subtility or whatver it is... apparently that helps too...but  i put 2 points in it, never saw anything helpful, so i didnt complete it..i have too many more aa's still to do, and getting summoned isnt a big issue for me, i tend to live through most of my summoned experiences
